Package env

Interface MapModel

All Known Implementing Classes:
BlackForestModel
public interface MapModel
The MapModel interface defines the behavior of the game map model. Implementing classes should manage the state of the map, including updating and rendering the map's elements based on agent interactions and environment changes.

The model should be able to update the map's state, as well as provide necessary information for rendering or simulating the game world.
